<h1>Time Card</h1>

 <table>
<TR><TH>Employee<TH>Month<TH>Payday<TH>Exception<TH>Dates</TR>
<TR><TD rowspan=4> <formvariable name=employee options=users> </formvariable>
    <TD rowspan=4> <formvariable name=paymonth options="01 02 03 04 05 06 07 08 09 10 11 12">&month; </formvariable>
    <TD rowspan=4> <formvariable name=payday options="15 30">&day; </formvariable>

<TD> Sick Days  <TD> <formvariable name=sick> </formvariable> </TR>
<TR><TD> Personal Holidays  <TD> <formvariable name=holiday> </formvariable>
</TR>
<TR><TD> Vacation Days  <TD> <formvariable name=vacation> </formvariable>
</TR>
<TR><TD> Other Days  <TD> <formvariable name=other> </formvariable> </TR>
</table>

<p>
Time cards for regular employees ("Exempt Personnel") are reported by
exception. If you did not miss any workdays this pay period, leave the dates
above blank and click on the Process button. Otherwise enter the dates missed
in the appropriate boxes and then click Process.
